---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Press" description="Latest news and media mentions of Severino Realty.">
  <section class="py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Press &amp; News</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6">Severino Realty has been featured in various media outlets for our market insights and customer service. Read some of our recent mentions below.</p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <article class="bg-neutral-100 p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Daily Nation – "Local Agency Shaping Nairobi’s Real Estate"</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">An interview with our founder about emerging trends in the Nairobi property market.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-neutral-100 p-6 rounded-md shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Business Daily – "How Technology Is Transforming Home Buying"</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">We share how we’re using digital tools to help buyers and sellers connect.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
